<m:mn> 1 </m:mn>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>

<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mo> ⇒ </m:mo>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> v </m:mi>
<m:mi> y </m:mi>
</m:msub>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:mn> 20 </m:mn>
<m:mspace width="2pt"/>
<m:mi> m </m:mi>
<m:mo> / </m:mo>
<m:mi> s </m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>

</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-79">
The resultant velocity, v, is given by :
</para>
<para id="element-80">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mi> v </m:mi>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
<m:msqrt>
<m:mo> ( </m:mo>
<m:msup>
<m:mrow>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> v </m:mi>
<m:mi> x </m:mi>
</m:msub>
